close_reason: "Resolved in PR #44 (13048461): replay/patch mechanics single-sourced in src/core/history/replay.ts (ReplayDocument, replayHash, normalizeReplayPatch*, toReplayDocument, tryApplyReplayPatch, verifyHistoryChain, reanchorHistoryEntries); history/restore/history-redact/history-repair share it. Per-command error-formatting wrappers kept local by design to preserve CLI error contracts. Full coverage gate + build green; no CLI output change."
